text: "Country Comes to Town" is a 2000 song by Toby Keith and is the third single from his fifth studio album How Do You Like Me Now?!. It went to number 54 in the United States and made number 4 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs chart and number 3 on the RPM Country Tracks chart. ==Notes== Category:2000 songs Category:Country songs Category:Toby Keith songs
title: Country Comes to Town
